Censabella teaching experience includes New School Drama, Actors Studio Drama School (where developed playwriting program Romulus Linney), Columbia University School Arts, Columbia College Undergraduate Writing Program, City University MFA Writing Program, The Sewanee Writers ' Conference, Summer Literary Seminars.
